A "swell" proposal Back in March, Miranda Kerr was spotted with some bling on her ring finger. But she swore she and Orlando weren't engaged. "No, we're not engaged. You can't always believe everything you read," she said to the press. "We were in Cannes at the film festival and it was so hot that my fingers were swelling. I was wearing it on that finger because that's the only one it would fit on. It was totally an innocent thing." They got hitched in secret four months later. Just saying.

