A rocker's promise Last month, Bret Michaels' on-again, off-again girlfriend was spotted wearing a ring. Bret went out of his way to explain that they aren't rushing to the altar. "No. We are not engaged yet. It's a work in progress," he said. "What happened is she has a beautiful promise ring. A promise ring, a friendship ring with benefits. So, it's-that's what we call it." I believe him just because I can hear the fear of commitment in his voice.

Model's ring is from a "friend" Bar Rafaeli was caught wearing an engagement ring a few months back. She said, "No, there wasn't [a proposal]. Let me explain: these rings, which are beautiful and made by a friend of mine, won't fit any other finger except this one." Or, uh, you could always wear the rings on your right hand? I bet we hear about her and Leonardo DiCaprio's wedding soon enough.

